'''御赐双龙宝星'''，是[[中国|中国]][[清朝|清朝]][[光绪|光绪]]七年（1882年2月7日）开始颁赠的宝星（即现在所称的[[勋章|勋章]]）；初期，它只是一种授予外国人的礼物，从1908年开始，它也授予清朝的官员。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://members.pcug.org.au/~phodge/Double%20Dragon.htm |title=Order of the Double Dragon - Shuang Lung Pao Hsing (The Imperial Order of the Double Dragon) |access-date=2010-09-16 |archive-date=2016-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313132826/http://members.pcug.org.au/~phodge/Double%20Dragon.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

寶星中心以雙龍為圖案，外形為星狀，鑲嵌珍寶，光芒奔射；用滿漢文書寫「御賜雙龍寶星」。双龙宝星分为五等，前三等又各分为三个品级：<ref>{{Cite magazine|url=https://www.drnh.gov.tw/var/file/3/1003/img/10/575112014.pdf|title=國史館「勳章的故事」展覽介紹|author=林本原|magazine=《國史研究通訊》|issue=第二期|publisher=[[國史館|國史館]]|date=2012-06-01|page=213|access-date=2018-09-27|archive-date=2022-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220201190355/https://www.drnh.gov.tw/var/file/3/1003/img/10/575112014.pdf}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Christopher Buyers|title=The Manchu Dynasty (Ta Ch'ing Ch'ao) Orders & Decorations|url=http://www.royalark.net/China/orders.htm|access-date=2010-09-16|archive-date=2021-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210619023636/https://royalark.net/China/orders.htm}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book | editor=邵之棠 | chapterurl=https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&chapter=528488 | title=《皇朝經世文統編》 | chapter=卷一百七　雜著部三 | access-date=2018-09-27 | archive-date=2021-03-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313122646/https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&chapter=528488 }}</ref>
